 /*DECLARATION OF VAR COMMON FOR ALL PROC'S INSIDE THE PROC MAIN      */
 /*BY DEFAULT, IT WILL BE OF AUTO   STORAGE CLASS  TYPE               */
 /*********************************************************************/
