USER DEFINED DATATYPES:
=======================
- PL1 allows us to create our own data types as references to built in data types
- DEFINE ALIAS & DEFINE ORDINAL are used to create user defined datatypes
- DEFINE ALIAS
  - It is used to create a synonym or alias for a set of attributes
- DEFINE ORDINAL
  - It is named set of ordered values
  - It is used to define ordinals
  - It is equal to ENUM in C++

